# {{ site.businessName }} — Sub-Metering Installation for Landlords

> {{ site.businessName }} installs certified electricity sub-meters in multi-unit rental properties across {{ site.serviceArea }}. Landlords with shared meters lose $300+ per month subsidizing tenants' hydro. We fix that.

## What We Do

{{ site.businessName }} installs Measurement Canada certified sub-meters that give each unit in a multi-unit property its own electricity meter. The meters clip onto existing wiring — no rewiring, no cutting, no damage to the property. Installation takes one day. Tenants pay for what they use. Landlords stop subsidizing hydro.

